{"tid":2125821,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"區議員借議辦搞罷工公投、初選 兩個月逾六萬元津貼被抽起","createTime":"2020-07-26T12:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T13:23:29.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a86d526fcc4ec1a8c3000a8717c32b59d9146b93","tid":2125821,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T12:36:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075852\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075852&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=5756a89f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075852&h=3291c316\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075852</a><br />\n<br />\n（獨媒特約報導）據悉，多名曾借出議員辦事處作民主派初選票站的區議員，均被抽起本月津貼。東區區議員郭志聰向《獨媒》表示，自己分別於上月20日及本月11及12日，借出議辦作罷工公投票站及的民主派初選票站，惟初選結束僅兩星期，他即遭秋後算賬，涉及兩個月、逾六萬元的區議員津貼被抽起。郭志聰批評政府「綑綁式」把整個月的津貼抽起，「係咪其餘28日都冇服務過街坊呢？」並反問，「咁建制派又可以搞撐《國安法》聯署？」"},{"pid":"4a2c4e77b2ac1c618479068ba771d38aef985b65","tid":2125821,"uid":43062,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T12:37:45.000Z","msg":"港共要玩野真係無處不在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇得JR"},{"pid":"61a26610a3cd62e23ffb19d0382682c0f716399f","tid":2125821,"uid":362935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T12:38:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aee1e1577c0698101f17ba24908ccf2ee37dceb9","tid":2125821,"uid":64953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T12:38:23.000Z","msg":"國際線見"},{"pid":"76edce4c7a07ad767dba04a4a3e63948f260f303","tid":2125821,"uid":174120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T12:44:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0b698de8c664f0b4306454e5466459bb42dd4002","tid":2125821,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T12:45:23.000Z","msg":"